			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Posterous is looking for a Head of Business Development to identify, qualify and close partnerships to accelerate the growth of Posterous Sites and Groups. You&rsquo;ll own partner identification, qualification and closing, manage our existing relationships and direct the roll-out and ongoing improvement of our self-service platform.</p>
<p>
	Qualified candidates will have a track record of success closing high impact deals, a deep background in both the web services and mobile industries and strong comfort level working at the strategic and tactical level within a start-up environment.</p>
<p>
	Requirements</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		5+ years of success in a business development role, at least two of which have been with a consumer facing start up.</li>
	<li>
		Excellent analytical skills</li>
	<li>
		Strong record of initiating and closing partnerships that align with strategic goals&nbsp;</li>
	<li>
		Impeccable communication skills</li>
	<li>
		B.A./B.S. with a strong academic record; MBA from a top tier business school preferred</li>
</ul>
<p>
	The ideal candidate will have the following qualities:</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Unquestionable integrity</li>
	<li>
		Quick learner with a thirst for understanding our technical stack</li>
	<li>
		Prior relevant relationships</li>
	<li>
		A sense of urgency in closing partnerships</li>
	<li>
		Highly organized &ndash; able to juggle multiple relationships</li>
	<li>
		A passion for Posterous products and consumer Internet products&nbsp;</li>
	<li>
		Team player &ndash; able to work effectively with multiple functions</li>
</ul>
<p>
	Posterous is an angel and VC-funded software startup in the heart of San Francisco&#39;s Mission district. We are a fast-moving 12 person company. Six of us are software engineers that build and run the whole site. We believe in a radically transparent and meritocratic system so that the best ideas always win.</p>
<p>
	Compensation includes full time salary, generous equity compensation plan, and benefits.</p>
<p>
	More info about us is available at:</p>
<p>
	http://posterous.com/jobs</p>
<p>
	To apply, visit posterous.theresumator.com and include a resume and why you&#39;d be a great fit for Posterous.</p>
